messages.name: Tyrion Lannister
messages.body: Never forget what you are, the rest of the world will not. Wear it like armor and it can never be used to hurt you.

messages.name: Daenerys Targaryen
messages.body: When my dragons are grown, we will take back what was stolen from me and destroy those who wronged me! We will lay waste to armies and burn cities to the ground!

messages.name: Sansa Stark
messages.body: Did you know about Ramsay? If you didn’t know, you’re an idiot. If you did know, you’re my enemy.

messages.name: Jon Snow
messages.body: Sometimes there Is no happy choice, only one less grievous than the others.

messages.name: Tyrion Lannister
messages.body: A mind needs books like a sword needs a whetstone.

messages.name: Arya Stark
messages.body: She blushed prettily. She did everything prettily, Arya thought with dull resentment.

messages.name: Sansa Stark
messages.body: I am Sansa Stark of Winterfell. This is my home. And you can’t frighten me.

messages.name: Jon Snow
messages.body: I do know some things, I know I love you. I know you love me. I have to go home now.
